Package: fairGNN
Title: Fairness-Aware Gated Neural Networks
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Rhys", "Holland", , "rhys.holland@icloud.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements a fairness-aware gated neural network (GNN) 
    architecture for predictive modelling with bias mitigation. 
    Includes tools for data preparation, model training, performance 
    assessment, expert analysis, and visualisation.
